---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<Layout>
  <div class="pt-24 md:pt-32 pb-16 px-4 md:px-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-mono tracking-tighter mb-6">
        About Thinkin' Rocks
      </h1>
      
      <!-- Main Content -->
      <div class="mb-16 fade-in">
        <p class="font-sans text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          Thinkin' Rocks is the playground we always wished existed.
        </p>
        <p class="font-sans text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          Finland has world-class students and a thriving startup scene, yet when it comes to hardware, access is 
          limited. Most students are still restricted to laptops, while peers abroad prototype with GPUs, humanoid 
          robots, and XR headsets. Too many bold ideas never move beyond a slide deck - and we believe that holds 
          Finland back.
        </p>
        <p class="font-sans text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          In 2025, with the support of Aaltoes - Europe's largest student-run entrepreneurship society and the 
          community behind Slush, Junction, and Kiuas - we launched Thinkin' Rocks: a student-driven technology 
          studio where anyone curious enough can get their hands on advanced tools. From Varjo XR headsets and 
          humanoid robots to Tenstorrent AI kits, FPGA boards, and Jetson-powered platforms, we make frontier 
          tech as accessible as a library book. Students learn by building - crashing code, fixing it, and working 
          side by side with engineers from companies like Varjo and Doublepoint.
        </p>
        <p class="font-sans text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          By opening access, we strengthen Finland's deep-tech pipeline: turning projects into prototypes, and 
          prototypes into startups. Our vision is bold - to become Finland's hub for applied innovation and fuel the 
          100x100 ambition: 100 deep-tech startups, each worth â‚¬100M.
        </p>
        <p class="font-sans text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          To reach that vision, we've set clear goals each year:
        </p>
        
        <!-- Goals Visualization -->
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-xl font-mono text-gray-900 mb-1">500+</div>
              <div class="font-sans text-sm text-gray-700">active contributors</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-xl font-mono text-gray-900 mb-1">10-15</div>
              <div class="font-sans text-sm text-gray-700">MVP prototypes</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-xl font-mono text-gray-900 mb-1">2,500+</div>
              <div class="font-sans text-sm text-gray-700">students reached</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-xl font-mono text-gray-900 mb-1">3-5</div>
              <div class="font-sans text-sm text-gray-700">new startups</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <p class="font-sans text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          The journey is already underway. Since our launch at Explore Aaltoes in September 2025, we've partnered 
          with Varjo, Alif Semiconductor, Tenstorrent, Doublepoint, and Booster Robotics, and hosted meetups with 
          80+ students and researchers. Today, world-class tools are no longer locked in labs - they're in student 
          hands.
        </p>
        <p class="font-sans text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          And this is only the start. We're expanding our hardware pool with neurowearables, humanoid robots, and 
          advanced AI compute, while running hackathons, build sprints, and demo days that turn ideas into working 
          prototypes.
        </p>
      </div>
 

        <!-- Partners Section -->
      <div class="mb-16 fade-in">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-mono mb-6 text-gray-900">Our Partners</h2>
        <p class="font-sans text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          We work with industry leaders to bring cutting-edge technology directly to students:
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 md:gap-8 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-3 md:p-4 rounded-lg text-center">
            <div class="w-24 h-16 sm:w-32 sm:h-20 md:w-40 md:h-24 mx-auto flex items-center justify-center">
              <img 
                src="/images/companies-logo/varjo.png" 
                alt="Varjo" 
                class="w-full h-full object-contain"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-3 md:p-4 rounded-lg text-center">
            <div class="w-24 h-16 sm:w-32 sm:h-20 md:w-40 md:h-24 mx-auto flex items-center justify-center">
              <img 
                src="/images/companies-logo/doublepoint.png" 
                alt="Doublepoint" 
                class="w-full h-full object-contain"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-3 md:p-4 rounded-lg text-center">
            <div class="w-24 h-16 sm:w-32 sm:h-20 md:w-40 md:h-24 mx-auto flex items-center justify-center">
              <img 
                src="/images/companies-logo/tenstorrent.webp" 
                alt="Tenstorrent" 
                class="w-full h-full object-contain"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-3 md:p-4 rounded-lg text-center">
            <div class="w-24 h-16 sm:w-32 sm:h-20 md:w-40 md:h-24 mx-auto flex items-center justify-center">
              <img 
                src="/images/companies-logo/Alif_Semiconductor_logo.webp" 
                alt="Alif Semiconductor" 
                class="w-full h-full object-contain"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-3 md:p-4 rounded-lg text-center">
            <div class="w-24 h-16 sm:w-32 sm:h-20 md:w-40 md:h-24 mx-auto flex items-center justify-center">
              <img 
                src="/images/companies-logo/booster_robotics.png" 
                alt="Booster Robotics" 
                class="w-full h-full object-contain"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
          <a 
            href="mailto:milana@thinkinrocks.com?subject=Partnership%20Opportunity&body=Hi%20Milana,%0D%0A%0D%0AI'm%20interested%20in%20exploring%20a%20partnership%20opportunity%20with%20Thinkin'%20Rocks.%0D%0A%0D%0ACompany:%20[Your%20Company]%0D%0ATechnology/Hardware:%20[What%20you%20can%20provide]%0D%0AContact:%20[Your%20contact%20information]%0D%0A%0D%0ABest%20regards,"
            class="block bg-gray-100 p-3 md:p-4 rounded-lg text-center hover:bg-gray-200 hover:border-gray-400 transition-colors"
          >
            <div class="w-24 h-16 sm:w-32 sm:h-20 md:w-40 md:h-24 mx-auto flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-mono text-gray-400">+</span>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
        

      <!-- Contact Section -->
      <div class="text-center fade-in">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="bg-indigo-600 h-fit translate-0.5">
            <a 
              href="https://discord.gg/5MEu6njksN" 
              class="bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600 inline-flex px-6 py-3 -translate-0.5 items-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap font-mono hover:bg-indigo-100 transition-colors"
            >
              Join Us
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-600 h-fit translate-0.5">
            <a 
              href="mailto:milana@thinkinrocks.com" 
              class="bg-gray-50 text-gray-600 inline-flex px-6 py-3 -translate-0.5 items-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap font-mono hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors"
            >
              Contact Us
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
